questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Software> . ?company a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Company> . ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/developer> ?company . ?company <http://dbpedia.org/property/foundation> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/California> }

questions.question: Which instruments does Cat Stevens play?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens> <http://dbpedia.org/property/instrument> ?uri }

questions.question: How many airlines are members of the Star Alliance?
questions.query: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) AS ?c) WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Airline> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/alliance> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Star_Alliance> }

questions.question: Give me all actors called Baldwin.
questions.query: PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbp:name ?name FILTER regex(?name, "Baldwin"). ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/occupation> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Actor> }

questions.question: Who wrote The Hunger Games?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hunger_Games> <http://dbpedia.org/property/author> ?uri }

questions.question: For which label did Elvis record his first album?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?x rdf:type dbo:Album ; dbo:artist res:Elvis_Presley ; dbo:releaseDate ?y ; dbo:recordLabel ?uri } ORDER BY ASC(?y) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

questions.question: Is Christian Bale starring in Batman Begins?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> ASK WHERE { res:Batman_Begins dbo:starring res:Christian_Bale }

questions.question: Where is the residence of the prime minister of Spain?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Spain> <http://dbpedia.org/property/residence> ?uri }

questions.question: Which actor was casted in the most movies?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Actor> . ?f <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Film> . ?f <http://dbpedia.org/property/starring> ?uri . } ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(DISTINCT(?f))) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

questions.question: Which countries have more than two official languages?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Country> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/officialLanguage> ?language } GROUP BY ?uri HAVING ( COUNT(?language) > 2 )

questions.question: Which countries have more than ten caves?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Country> . ?cave a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Cave> { ?cave <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location> ?uri } UNION { ?cave <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location> ?loc . ?loc <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country> ?uri } } GROUP BY ?uri HAVING ( COUNT(?cave) > 10 )

questions.question: Show me all songs from Bruce Springsteen released between 1980 and 1990.
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/MusicalWork> . ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/artist> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Springsteen> . ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/releaseDate> ?date . FILTER (?date >= '1980-01-01'^^xsd:date && ?date <= '1990-12-31'^^xsd:date) }

questions.question: Which television shows were created by John Cleese?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/TelevisionShow> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/creator> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Cleese> }

questions.question: When did Latvia join the EU?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?date WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia> <http://dbpedia.org/property/establishedDate> ?date }

questions.question: Which soccer players were born on Malta?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/SoccerPlayer> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta> }

questions.question: How many politicians graduated from Columbia University?
questions.query: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) AS ?c) WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/profession> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Politician> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/almaMater> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_University> }

questions.question: Give me the birthdays of all actors of the television show Charmed.
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?date WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charmed> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/starring> ?actor . ?actor <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthDate> ?date }

questions.question: Which telecommunications organizations are located in Belgium?
questions.query: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) AS ?c) WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Organisation> { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/industry> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telecommunication> } UNION { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/property/industry> ?industry FILTER regex(?industry, "Telecommunications") } { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium> } UNION { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/property/locationCountry> "Belgium"@en } }

questions.question: Give me a list of all lakes in Denmark.
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Lake> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark> } UNION { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/LakesOfDenmark> } }

questions.question: How many children does Eddie Murphy have?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?n WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddie_Murphy> <http://dbpedia.org/property/children> ?n }

questions.question: Show me all English Gothic buildings in Kent.
questions.query: SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Building> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/architecturalStyle> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_Gothic_architecture> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kent> }

questions.question: Who is the manager of Real Madrid?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Real_Madrid_CF> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/manager> ?uri }

questions.question: In which countries can you pay using the West African CFA franc?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/currency> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_African_CFA_franc> }

questions.question: Which holidays are celebrated around the world?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Holiday }

questions.question: What is the longest river?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/River> { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/length> ?l } UNION { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/property/length> ?l } } ORDER BY DESC(?l) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

questions.question: Which organizations were founded in 1930?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Organisation> { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/formationYear> ?date } UNION { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/foundingYear> ?date } FILTER regex(?date, "^1930") }

questions.question: What is the birth name of Angela Merkel?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?string WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Merkel> <http://dbpedia.org/property/birthName> ?string }

questions.question: Who has Tom Cruise been married to?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/spouse> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise> }

questions.question: Which weapons did Heckler & Koch develop?
questions.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Weapon> ; <http://dbpedia.org/property/designer> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heckler_&_Koch> }

questions.question: What is the smallest city by area in Germany?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> SELECT ?city WHERE { ?m skos:broader dbc:Cities_in_Germany . ?city dct:subject ?m ; dbo:areaTotal ?area } ORDER BY ?area LIMIT 1

questions.question: What are the official languages of the Philippines?
questions.query: PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Philippines dbp:recognizedRegionalLanguages ?uri }

questions.question: Which movies starring Brad Pitt were directed by Guy Ritchie?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Film ; dbo:starring res:Brad_Pitt ; dbo:director res:Guy_Ritchie }
